snippet.title: Mushroom Picnic Party Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Help find little mushrooms and prepare for an epic picnic party in this cute hand-drawn hidden object game! Explore 13 locations, chat with townsfolk, and solve puzzles!

Available on Steam: https://steampowered.com/app/2469280/Mushroom_Picnic_Party/
